provider "github" {
  token = "token of the github"
}
resource "github_repository" "example" {
  name        = "example"
  description = "This repo is created using terraform"

  visibility = "public"
}


NOTE:Token in github is generated by using the following steps
CLick on profile <  settings <  Developer settings  < personal access tokens  <  tokens classic  <   Generate new token
